thread.title_full: Herinneringen Op Linnen Beoordeeld door Ugo

author: Ugo
title: Ugo
text:
I am very happy with the after sales service. One of the print had a mount completly missplaced and they resolved my problem quickly.
HD metal print is very intersting and very few online service actually print this new technology in Europe. It's very popular in the US and "Herinneringen Op Linnen" offers nice prices and the standard quality i am looking for.
I do recommand this online print service. And they won a new costumer for sure.
